    "Information may be embedded within paragraphs or other textual content, necessitating more complex extraction methods.",
    "Sotheby's utilises an Apollo GraphQL Database for systematic data organisation, allowing straightforward data access via the database Application Programming Interface (API), or through uncomplicated scraping methods.",
